{"title":"IF语句","uid":"01b3914bcd189eedbd605f187179d24e","slug":"IF语句","date":"2023-07-31T14:58:51.000Z","updated":"2023-07-31T15:44:50.159Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/IF语句.json","keywords":"serverDream's blog","cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"IF语句\"><a href=\"#IF语句\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"IF语句\"></a>IF语句</h1><h2 id=\"定义\"><a href=\"#定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"定义\"></a>定义</h2><p>C++的if语句是用来<strong>判定所给的条件是否满足</strong>，并根据判断的结果<strong>true</strong>(真)或<strong>false</strong>(假)决定执行哪一步。</p>\n<h2 id=\"用法\"><a href=\"#用法\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"用法\"></a>用法</h2><h3 id=\"if如果那么\"><a href=\"#if如果那么\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if如果那么\"></a>if如果那么</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>条件集<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//条件集:由单个或多个条件组成,条件也可以是bool变量</span>\n    语句集<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//语句集:由单个或多个语句组成</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>如果<strong>条件集</strong>成立-&gt;执行<strong>语句集</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"if-else如果那么、否则\"><a href=\"#if-else如果那么、否则\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if-else如果那么、否则\"></a>if-else如果那么、否则</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>条件集<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    语句集<span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    语句集<span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>如果<strong>条件集</strong>成立-&gt;执行<strong>语句集1</strong></p>\n<p>如果<strong>条件集</strong>不成立-&gt;执行<strong>语句集2</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"if-elseif-else如果那么、否则如果、否则\"><a href=\"#if-elseif-else如果那么、否则如果、否则\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if-elseif-else如果那么、否则如果、否则\"></a>if-elseif-else如果那么、否则如果、否则</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>条件集<span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    语句集<span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>条件集<span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//可嵌套多个else if</span>\n    语句集<span class=\"token number\">2</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    语句集<span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>如果<strong>条件集1</strong>成立-&gt;执行<strong>语句集1</strong></p>\n<p>如果<strong>条件集1</strong>不成立-&gt;如果<strong>条件集2</strong>成立-&gt;执行<strong>语句集2</strong></p>\n<p>如果<strong>条件集1</strong>不成立-&gt;如果<strong>条件集2</strong>不成立-&gt;执行<strong>语句集3</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"练习讲解\"><a href=\"#练习讲解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"练习讲解\"></a>练习讲解</h2><h3 id=\"二的倍数\"><a href=\"#二的倍数\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二的倍数\"></a>二的倍数</h3><h4 id=\"题目描述\"><a href=\"#题目描述\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"题目描述\"></a>题目描述</h4><p>判断n是否为二的倍数</p>\n<h4 id=\"输入格式\"><a href=\"#输入格式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输入格式\"></a>输入格式</h4><p>一个整数n</p>\n<h4 id=\"输出格式\"><a href=\"#输出格式\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"输出格式\"></a>输出格式</h4><p>判断n是否为<strong>二的倍数</strong>，是的输出“<strong>Yes</strong>”，否则输出“<strong>No</strong>”</p>\n<h4 id=\"样例输入1\"><a href=\"#样例输入1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输入1\"></a>样例输入1</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-txt\" data-language=\"txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">2<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"样例输出1\"><a href=\"#样例输出1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输出1\"></a>样例输出1</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-txt\" data-language=\"txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">Yes<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"样例输入2\"><a href=\"#样例输入2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输入2\"></a>样例输入2</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-txt\" data-language=\"txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">3<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"样例输出2\"><a href=\"#样例输出2\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"样例输出2\"></a>样例输出2</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-txt\" data-language=\"txt\"><code class=\"language-txt\">No<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"代码\"><a href=\"#代码\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"代码\"></a>代码</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-cpp\" data-language=\"cpp\"><code class=\"language-cpp\"><span class=\"token macro property\"><span class=\"token directive-hash\">#</span><span class=\"token directive keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"token string\">&lt;iostream></span></span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">namespace</span> std<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> <span class=\"token function\">main</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">int</span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    cin <span class=\"token operator\">>></span> n<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>n <span class=\"token operator\">%</span> <span class=\"token number\">2</span> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//如果n除2余0(是偶数)</span>\n        cout <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Yes\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//则输出\"Yes\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#123;</span>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//否则</span>\n        cout <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"No\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&lt;&lt;</span> endl<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"token comment\">//输出\"No\"</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">&#125;</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"课后作业\"><a href=\"#课后作业\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"课后作业\"></a>课后作业</h2><p>不看答案写出题目<strong>2的倍数</strong>。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"IF语句定义C++的if语句是用来判定所给的条件是否满足，并根据判断的结果true(真)或false(假)决定执行哪一步。 用法if如果那么if(条件集) &#123; //条件集:由单个或多个条件组成,条件也可以是bool变量 语句集; //语句集:由单个或多个语句组成 &#1...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":966,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"IF语句","slug":"IF语句","count":1,"path":"api/tags/IF语句.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#IF%E8%AF%AD%E5%8F%A5\"><span class=\"toc-text\">IF语句</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%94%A8%E6%B3%95\"><span class=\"toc-text\">用法</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#if%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">if如果那么</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#if-else%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E3%80%81%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">if-else如果那么、否则</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#if-elseif-else%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E9%82%A3%E4%B9%88%E3%80%81%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99%E5%A6%82%E6%9E%9C%E3%80%81%E5%90%A6%E5%88%99\"><span class=\"toc-text\">if-elseif-else如果那么、否则如果、否则</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%BB%83%E4%B9%A0%E8%AE%B2%E8%A7%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">练习讲解</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%80%